            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 上星期舉行了發布會，席間公佈了 iPhone 16 及 16 Pro 系列、全新 AirPods 4 主動降噪版、Apple Watch Series 10、Apple Watch Ultra 2 黑色鈦金屬版等，以及全新手機套和 MagSafe 配件等。今日起全部秋季新產品已登陸香港全線 6 間 Apple Store ，有興趣看看實物的朋友可以親臨各 Apple Store。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264449" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8275-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8275-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8275.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲iPhone 16 全顏色已登陸 Apple Store</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264450" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8276-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8276-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8276.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲iPhone 16 Pro 四款鈦金屬色亦已於 Apple Store 展出</p><p>Apple Intelligence 將於 10 月隨 iOS 18.1、iPad 18.1 與 macOS Sequoia 15.1 一併推出，更多功能亦緊隨數月內登場。此為將生成模型的強勁效能與個人背景相結合的的個人智能系統，為用戶帶來極為實用且相關的智能功能。</p><p>Apple Intelligence 率先推出美國英文版，並將於明年擴展至更多語言，包括中文、日文、韓文。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264451" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8278-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8278-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8278.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全新 Apple Watch Series 10</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264452" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8279-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8279-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8279.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全面採用 USB-C 的 5 款新顏色 AirPods Max 亦已於 Apple Store 展出<br />
（午夜黑、藍色、紫色、橙色和星光金）</p><p>下面為 Apple 用家到訪 Apple Store 試玩新 iPhone 16、iPhone 16 Pro 系列手機的盛況：</p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="Apple Store 20 Sep 2024-1" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1011243091?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="Apple Store 20 Sep 2024-2" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1011243126?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8273" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1011243152?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/07/apple-store-hints-at-iphone-16-release-date/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">瑞典 Apple Store 公佈開業安排，被指配合 iPhone 16 系列首賣日</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/21/apple-kuala-lumpur-store/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Store 終於登陸馬來西亞   Apple 吉隆坡店明日開幕</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/20/apple-2024-fall-items-all-iphone-16-in-apple-store-now/software/ios-app/">香港 Apple 秋季新產品今日開賣　iPhone 16 全顏色、AirPod 4 陳列品登陸全線 Apple Store</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
