            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日 iPhone 16 正式開賣，雖然今年炒風不算熱烈，放機熱點旺角先達廣場仍見人龍，有大批<span class="s1">朋友排隊放機。差價最大的是 iPhone 16 Pro Max 1TB 的沙漠色，收購價比原價多 2,300 元，其次是 512 GB 沙漠色 iPhone 16 Pro Max，比原價差距逾 2,050 元。iPhone 16 Pro 部分型號「炒燶」，收購價格僅為原價加一蚊。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264422" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6572-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6572-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6572.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264431" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6559-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6559-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6559.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264432" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6565-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6565-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6565.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264425" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/6298716840238628260-436x580.jpg" alt="" width="436" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/6298716840238628260-436x580.jpg 436w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/6298716840238628260.jpg 676w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 436px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264423" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6576-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6576-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6576.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264424" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6577-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6577-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6577.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264428" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6591-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6591-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_6591.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 192px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 10%; height: 24px;"></td><td style="width: 10%; text-align: center;"><strong>原價</strong></td><td style="width: 20%; height: 24px; text-align: center;"><strong>黑色</strong></td><td style="width: 20%; height: 24px; text-align: center;"><strong>白色</strong></td><td style="width: 20%; height: 24px; text-align: center;"><strong>沙漠色</strong></td><td style="width: 20%; height: 24px; text-align: center;"><strong>原色</strong></td></tr><tr><td style="width: 100%; text-align: left;" colspan="6"><strong>Pro</strong></td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 10%; height: 24px;">128 GB</td><td style="width: 10%; text-align: center;">8,599</td><td style="w